      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document describes the base-level server-based sorting and threading extensions to the IMAP protocol.  These extensions provide substantial performance improvements for IMAP clients that offer sorted and threaded views. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
